    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/victor_lavalle_734602",
        "quote": "Our family suffers from a hereditary condition called, generally, mental illness. Specifically, multiple family members in successive generations have suffered from either bipolar disorder or schizophrenia.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Victor LaValle",
            "url": "/quotes/victor_lavalle_734602"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Generations",
                "url": "/topics/generations"
            },
            {
                "name": "Mental",
                "url": "/topics/mental"
            },
            {
                "name": "Suffers",
                "url": "/topics/suffers"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/victor_lavalle_734603",
        "quote": "I realise I might pass down an incurable illness to my son, but living based on what might go wrong seems like less and less of a life as I get older. The one thing I can try to control is whether I teach my child to be ruled by anxiety, by fear. That's something that gets passed down, too.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Victor LaValle",
            "url": "/quotes/victor_lavalle_734603"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Life",
                "url": "/topics/life"
            },
            {
                "name": "I Can",
                "url": "/topics/i_can"
            },
            {
                "name": "Down",
                "url": "/topics/down"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/victor_lavalle_734604",
        "quote": "I hadn't stopped fearing the chance of passing on an illness, but that fear had become balanced by the observation that being ill wasn't the same as being beaten.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Victor LaValle",
            "url": "/quotes/victor_lavalle_734604"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Chance",
                "url": "/topics/chance"
            },
            {
                "name": "Observation",
                "url": "/topics/observation"
            },
            {
                "name": "Stopped",
                "url": "/topics/stopped"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/victor_lavalle_734605",
        "quote": "One of the things that doesn't come up as much as it should, especially in literary fiction, is this idea of faith and God... I feel like those are things that should be wrestled with... because they are such an integral part of our community on every level.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Victor LaValle",
            "url": "/quotes/victor_lavalle_734605"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Fiction",
                "url": "/topics/fiction"
            },
            {
                "name": "One Of The Things",
                "url": "/topics/one_of_the_things"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/victor_lavalle_734606",
        "quote": "People use the notion of God to bully people and hurt people, when we can use the concept to respect and uplift.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Victor LaValle",
            "url": "/quotes/victor_lavalle_734606"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Uplift",
