    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/victor_lavalle_734611",
        "quote": "There's the wonder of being able to do research from your own living room, of course. I do find that my biggest research issue, though, is how to frame my questions.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Victor LaValle",
            "url": "/quotes/victor_lavalle_734611"
