    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/victor_lavalle_734621",
        "quote": "Shirley Jackson enjoyed notoriety and commercial success within her lifetime, and yet it still hardly seems like enough for a writer so singular. When I meet readers and other writers of my generation, I find that mentioning her is like uttering a holy name.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Victor LaValle",
            "url": "/quotes/victor_lavalle_734621"
        },
