                "url": "/topics/shirley"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/victor_lavalle_734624",
        "quote": "'The Ballad of Black Tom' was written, in part, during the latest round of arguments about H. P. Lovecraft's legacy as both a great writer and a prejudiced man. I grew up worshipping the guy, so this issue felt quite personal to me.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Victor LaValle",
            "url": "/quotes/victor_lavalle_734624"
